title: Bob Weir, Robinson, and Greene - 2011-08-20 - Rocky Mountain
description:
WRG - Bob Weir, Chris Robinson, & Jackie Greene

Rocky Mountain Folks Festival
Lyons, CO 
2011-08-20


Outstanding Audience recording!  Almost sounds like a Matrix recording.  Feels like here there man!

Sennheiser MKH800 Mics (Cards) > Sound Devices 722 @ 24/44.1 
Recorded from right front corner of SBD; mics approx 10 feet high. Dither to 16/44.1 with Cool Edit 2000 
Track using CD Wave Editor 


01. warmup / tuning
02. New Speedway Boogie
03. Friend Of The Devil
04. Ramble On Rose
05. When I Paint My Masterpiece
06. Catfish John
07. Tell Me Mama, Tell Me Right
08. Appaloosa
09. Jack Of Diamonds
10. Sugaree
11. Bird Song
12. Peggy-O
13. Uncle John's Band
14. China Cat Sunflower
15. Ripple



Length = 122 minutes (1 set) 
If you want to burn to two CD's, a suggestion is CD 1 = Tracks 1-9, CD 2 = Tracks 10-15
